YouTube content creator Mpoomy Ledwaba has finally secured office space for her business. Ledwaba took to social media to share how she thought she was crazy for getting an office for her business Wisdom Wellness and also growing it. She wrote that she realises that there has not been a day that she has not worried about whether she was going to make money, and what her team would do daily. Ledwaba, who recently celebrated six-year anniversary of marital bliss with her husband Brenden, said she trusts God in everything and follows her gut, noting that her office space would be up and running on March 4.  Also Read: Brenden and Mpoomy celebrate six years of marital bliss For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.